    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How do I determine my bangle size?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Unlike bracelets which are measured by wrist circumference, bangles are measured by the size of your hand (the knuckles) to ensure they can slide on. </p><p>We can measure your hand in-store to find the perfect diameter for a comfortable and secure fit. </p><p><a href=\"/blogs/guide-jewellery-sizing-guide/bracelet-size-guide\" title=\"How to Measure for Bracelets and Bangles\">View our Bracelet Sizing Guide</a></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Can I wear a tennis bracelet every day?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>High-quality diamond tennis bracelets set in platinum or 18ct gold are durable enough for daily wear. </p><p>However, we recommend regular checks of the clasp and settings (which we offer as a service) to ensure stones remain secure during active daily use.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "My bracelet clasp is loose, can you fix it?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, absolutely. A loose clasp is a common issue that can often be tightened or adjusted. </p><p>If the internal mechanism is worn, we can replace the entire clasp to ensure your bracelet is secure again.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What areas do you cover for Home Visits?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Our home visit service primarily covers Chichester and the immediate surrounding areas in West Sussex. </p><p>This service is ideal for clients who prefer the privacy and comfort of their own home for consultations or valuations. Please contact us to check availability for your specific location.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_BRezAN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Do I need an appointment to view wristwear?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>You are welcome to browse our collection at any time. However, for bespoke commissions or to view specific high-value pieces, we recommend booking an appointment for a home visit so we can have everything ready for you.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "accordion_GhRGXt",
        "accordion_HmVJLJ",
